墙的解决方法</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Obsidian-%E7%9A%84%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Obsidian 的配置</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Typora-1\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Typora</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Usage%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Usage——使用</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE\"><span class=\"toc-text\">截图</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%8B%96%E6%8B%BD\"><span class=\"toc-text\">拖拽</span></a></li></ol></li></ol>","author":{"name":"司空绝洛","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://s1.ax1x.com/2023/03/28/pp6IgyQ.jpg","link":"/","description":"浮生若梦，为欢几何","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{"title":"因未完全卸载导致的npm error EEXIST","uid":"02b162bfeafa9edce78b0e44f29c6cee","slug":"因未完全卸载导致的npm-error-EEXIST","date":"2020-04-18T11:48:28.000Z","updated":"2020-07-31T13:39:26.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/因未完全卸载导致的npm-error-EEXIST.json","cover":"https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/07/31/a1KLGj.png","text":"在安装PicGo-Core的时候，因为一直安装不了插件，于是导致我经常安装卸载PicGo-Core。 在某次安装的时候突然失败，上网查了一下原因，说是拒绝安装。 思考了一下，觉得有两种原因： 第一种，没有管理员权限 第二种，后台程序占用文件 然而解决这两个因素后，PicGo仍然安...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":221,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"Error","slug":"Error","count":1,"path":"api/categories/Error.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"PicGo","slug":"PicGo","count":2,"path":"api/tags/PicGo.json"},{"name":"npm","slug":"npm","count":1,"path":"api/tags/npm.json"},{"name":"Error","slug":"Error","count":1,"path":"api/tags/Error.json"}],"author":{"name":"司空绝洛","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://s1.ax1x.com/2023/03/28/pp6IgyQ.jpg","link":"/","description":"浮生若梦，为欢几何","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"feature":true},"next_post":{"title":"github + hexo博客搭建教程","uid":"bbd723d7a030c0131f233ffce27b57ad","slug":"github-hexo博客搭建教程","date":"2020-04-05T05:35:19.000Z","updated":"2020-04-18T08:33:27.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/github-hexo博客搭建教程.json","cover":"https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/04/05/GDCgZn.jpg","text":"Introduction——前言托更了很久，我一点不好意思都没有[手动滑稽]，我想应该没有人等着我的教程的吧。之所以这时才做这教程，是因为我准备开启新项目了，如果还不填坑的话，坑就越来越多，然后就不想填了。为了避免这种情况，所以我决定先填了这坑，再开新坑。 本篇文章将会一步步教你...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"5.8k","symbolsTime":"5 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"博客","slug":"博客","count":2,"path":"api/categories/博客.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"教程","slug":"教程","count":3,"path":"api/tags/教程.json"},{"name":"博客","slug":"博客","count":2,"path":"api/tags/博客.json"},{"name":"Hexo","slug":"Hexo","count":1,"path":"api/tags/Hexo.json"}],"author":{"name":"司空绝洛","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://s1.ax1x.com/2023/03/28/pp6IgyQ.jpg","link":"/","description":"浮生若梦，为欢几何","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}}}}